QID4.QuestionText:
Kashinath, 
 
Thank you for taking the time to complete this one page survey.
 
Within this voluntary survey, we would like to capture your feedback across a number of areas including your job, the workplace, your colleagues and your vision for the future. 
 
No matter what brand, agency or company you work in within Publicis Groupe, your feedback matters to us.
 
The feedback you provide only helps make your company and Publicis Groupe a great place to be for you and your colleagues far and wide.
 
Please note, your feedback will remain confidential, and will only be reported on and viewable at a consolidated level. If you have any questions or concerns regarding this survey, please reach out to a member of your talent team.
 
Merci

QID5.QuestionText: Is there anything else you would like to share with us?
QID5.Value: False commitments are being made for onsite travel in some big FS Banking projects to each and every developer which are not getting fulfilled. This way leadership is impacting the business badly. People are leaving because of these commitments. Till now around 6-7 members of our team has left and few are about to leave or serving notice period. Client has asked our competitors who are working for same client with us to increase their resources. Someone needs to look into this. Since last year I was told for onsite travel and they are not able to fulfill it. Complaining doesn't help at Publicis Sapient is what I felt in last 6 months. No one takes compains/concerns seriously.
